name: Db8Thyme
tagline: A simple debate timer for Public Forum debate.
body:
### Db8Thyme
It's a pretty timer, not much else to say?

### Authors and Contributors
Adam Towers (@Zarkoix) wrote Db8Thyme because he was bored and the debate timer in the chrome add-on store isn't very pretty.

### Support or Contact
Having trouble with Deb8Thyme? Check out the code and fix it yourself with a pull request, or make an issue and I'll get around to it when I can.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
